{"id":"13hd0wi5","parent_id":"2evkv6xf","name":"Phase 0.5 — Monorepo restructure (Vite+ workspace template)","description":"CONTEXT: Convert the flat single-package repo into a Vite+ / Bun-workspace monorepo so the client and the coming Bun server can share one sim + protocol (packages/shared). Based on the Vite+ monorepo template at node_modules/vite-plus/templates/monorepo. This is a MECHANICAL move with NO logic change — kept separate from the Phase 1 sim extraction so the diff reads as \"paths moved, behavior identical\". Sequenced AFTER Phase 0 (the fixed-timestep refactor is easier in the flat layout and reveals the real sim seam) and BEFORE Phase 1.\n\nINVESTIGATE / DO: relocate the current src/ -> apps/client/ (three.js, Preact, GLB/OGG assets, wrangler.jsonc); add root package.json workspaces [packages/*, apps/*, tools/*] + scripts (ready: vp check && vp run -r test && vp run -r build); root vite.config.ts with run.cache + shared fmt/lint and OVERRIDES per package (client: preact/glsl rules; server: env node); move app-specific vite config (rapier optimizeDeps include, rolldown vendor code-splitting for rapier/three, glsl plugin, assetsInclude glb/ogg, server.allowedHosts) into apps/client/vite.config.ts; keep #/* subpath imports per-package; confirm fallow audit + the GitHub Actions CI paths still resolve across the workspace.\n\nDO NOT scaffold a fresh repo with vp create — adopt the template structure into the existing repo to preserve git history, the tuned vite.config, and wrangler. Template ships pnpm/yarn catalog variants; we stay on Bun workspaces (package.json workspaces field).\n\nOPEN QUESTIONS FOR THE USER: app dir name (apps/client vs apps/web); whether the Cloudflare matchmaker Worker becomes apps/matchmaker now or waits for Phase 7.\n\nDONE WHEN: vp check, vp test, and vp build all pass from the new layout with the app under apps/client and an empty packages/shared placeholder; git history preserved; the running game behaves identically.","priority":1,"completed":true,"result":"Monorepo restructure: app moved to apps/client (pure git-mv renames), empty packages/shared placeholder, root Bun workspace + shared tsconfig.base.json, and uniform fmt/lint/typecheck/test/fallow gating across all packages. PR #24 (green, rebased onto main, in final review).","metadata":null,"created_at":"2026-06-26T16:49:27.917Z","updated_at":"2026-06-27T04:01:52.449Z","started_at":"2026-06-26T20:58:20.062Z","completed_at":"2026-06-27T04:01:52.449Z","blockedBy":[],"blocks":[],"children":[]}
