{"id":"tzffvzms","parent_id":"zgbnfktr","name":"Wire CI and quality tooling","description":"Milestone: bring greglinscheid.com up to the same quality-gate bar as vilos92.com (Ox/Vite+ stack) with gdex-level Fallow strictness.\n\n## Goal\n\nA fresh agent should be able to clone the repo, run the validation loop, and see the same CI jobs pass locally that GitHub Actions runs.\n\n## Copy from vilos92.com (Ox / Vite+)\n\n### package.json scripts\nAdd (mirror vilos92.com):\n- `fmt:check`: `vp fmt --check`\n- `lint`: `vp lint`\n- `typecheck`: `tsc --noEmit`\n- `test`: `vp test`\n- `check`: `vp check`\n- `fallow`: `fallow --summary`\n- `fallow:audit`: `fallow audit`\nKeep existing Astro/`prepare` scripts. Add `trustedDependencies: [\"fallow\"]`.\n\n### devDependencies\n- `fallow` (pin same major as gdex, e.g. `2.66.1`)\n- `typescript` (compatible with Astro 6 / Node >=22)\n\nRun `bun install` after edits.\n\n### vite.config.ts\nExpand `fmt` block — copy vilos92 `REPO_TS_FMT_OPTIONS` and add **`sortPackageJson: true`** (vilos92 has `sortImports` but not package.json sort yet; enable both here):\n- singleQuote, semi, trailingComma none, printWidth 110, tabWidth 2, bracketSpacing false, arrowParens avoid\n- `sortImports: true`, `sortPackageJson: true`\nExpand `lint` block — match vilos92:\n- `options: { typeAware: true, typeCheck: true }`\n- rules: `curly: ['error', 'all']`, `'no-nested-ternary': 'error'`\nKeep `staged: { '*': 'vp check --fix' }`.\nAdd `test` block if needed for `vp test` (vilos92 uses `include: ['src/**/*.test.ts']`; passWithNoTests ok until tests exist).\n\n### tsconfig.json\nKeep `extends: astro/tsconfigs/strict`. Ensure `tsc --noEmit` works — add vilos92-style strictness if missing: `noUnusedLocals`, `noUnusedParameters`, `noFallthroughCasesInSwitch`, `noEmit: true`.\n\n### AGENTS.md\nKeep Vite+ boilerplate. Append agent notes section modeled on vilos92.com AGENTS.md:\n- Validation loop: `vp check` → `vp test` → `bun run fallow:audit`\n- CI job → local command mapping table\n- Fallow guidance (from gdex AGENTS.md): fix or add entry, no greenwash; ask before baselines/ignores\n\n## Copy from gdex (Fallow policy)\n\n### .fallowrc.jsonc\nCopy gdex full `rules` block (all `error`). Set `entry` for this Astro repo — start with any real JS/TS ship surfaces under `src/` (e.g. future layouts/components); if the tree is `.astro`-only, pick entries fallow can reach or add a minimal TS module and document in AGENTS.md. Do **not** copy gdex `ignoreDependencies` unless needed.\n\n### .fallow/ baselines (empty to start)\n- `.fallow/.gitignore` → `*` (match gdex)\n- `.fallow/health-baseline.json` → `{\"runtime_coverage_findings\":[],\"target_keys\":[]}`\n- `.fallow/dupes-baseline.json` → `{\"clone_groups\":[]}`\n\n## CI (copy shape from vilos92.com)\n\nCreate `.github/workflows/continuous-integration.yaml` with jobs: **fmt**, **lint**, **typecheck**, **test**, **fallow** (skip gdex rust jobs and vilos92 builds.yaml Tauri stuff).\n\nCreate `.github/actions/install-bun-and-dependencies/action.yaml` — bun cache + `bun install --frozen-lockfile`. Prefer gdex pinned action SHAs (`checkout@v6`, etc.) over vilos92 floating `@v4` if easy.\n\nFallow job needs `fetch-depth: 0` and:\n`bun run fallow:audit -- --base ${{ github.event.pull_request.base.sha || 'origin/main' }}`\n\n## Division of labor (do not duplicate)\n\n| Concern | Tool |\n|---|---|\n| Format, import sort, package.json sort | Oxfmt (`vp fmt` / `fmt` in vite.config.ts) |\n| In-file lint + types | Oxlint/tsgolint (`vp lint`, `typeCheck: true`) |\n| Standalone CI typecheck | `tsc --noEmit` |\n| Unused exports, deps, files, circular imports | Fallow (`fallow:audit`) |\n\nOxlint does **not** replace Fallow for cross-file unused exports.\n\n## Verify before completing\n\n1. `bun install`\n2. `vp check`\n3. `bun run typecheck`\n4. `bun run test` (may pass with no tests)\n5. `bun run fallow:audit`\n6. `bun run fmt:check` and `bun run lint` individually (CI parity)\n\nDo **not** commit unless the user asks. Do **not** start this dex task unless asked.","priority":1,"completed":true,"result":"Wired CI and quality gates: package scripts (fmt/lint/typecheck/test/check/fallow), vite.config.ts fmt+lint rules, tsconfig strictness, gdex-style .fallowrc + baselines, src/site.ts entry, GitHub Actions (fmt/lint/typecheck/test/fallow), consolidated AGENTS.md. All local checks pass; committed on main (bd65de6) and pushed to origin.","metadata":null,"created_at":"2026-06-07T16:07:15.670Z","updated_at":"2026-06-07T16:17:41.216Z","started_at":"2026-06-07T16:07:45.079Z","completed_at":"2026-06-07T16:17:41.216Z","blockedBy":[],"blocks":["lbyqyqsy"],"children":[]}
